OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1778170273
OL,3,CDeath of girl, 12, crushed by falling
OL,4,Ctree branch an accident, coroner rules
OL,6,FThe death of a 12-year-old girl after
OL,7,Fshe was hit by a falling branch while
OL,8,Fplaying on a rope swing was an
OL,9,Faccident, a coroner has ruled.
OL,11,FBrooke Wiggins died days before her
OL,12,F13th birthday on November 9 2024 in
OL,13,FBanstead, Surrey, after she fell from
OL,14,Fa rope swing attached to a large
OL,15,Fbranch of a tree which suddenly
OL,16,Fsnapped off and crushed her beneath
OL,17,Fits weight, South London Coroner's
OL,18,FCourt heard.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/8
