OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1778170273
OL,3,CDeath of girl, 12, crushed by falling
OL,4,Ctree branch an accident, coroner rules
OL,6,FAssistant coroner Ivor Collett said
OL,7,FSurrey County Council, which was
OL,8,Fresponsible for maintaining the tree,
OL,9,Fhad been criticised over how it
OL,10,Finspected the safety of trees, but
OL,11,Fconcluded it could not have reasonably
OL,12,Fbeen expected to do more to prevent it
OL,13,Ffrom happening.
OL,15,FMr Collett said: "I see what happened
OL,16,Fon the awful day of Brooke's death as
OL,17,Fan accident which was not readily
OL,18,Fforeseeable by either of the local
OL,19,Fauthorities involved.
OL,26,@wD@ROU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1778170273
OL,3,CDeath of girl, 12, crushed by falling
OL,4,Ctree branch an accident, coroner rules
OL,6,F"I find that they, and Surrey County
OL,7,FCouncil in particular, had reasonable
OL,8,Fsystems in place. Bearing in mind
OL,9,Ftheir duties and the risks and the
OL,10,Fpublic resources they have to manage,
OL,11,Fthey could not reasonably be expected
OL,12,Fto have done more in a way which would
OL,13,Fhave prevented this terrible accident."
OL,15,FThe inquest previously heard the tree
OL,16,Fhad been reviewed by Surrey County
OL,17,FCouncil in May 2022.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@gO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1778170273
OL,3,CDeath of girl, 12, crushed by falling
OL,4,Ctree branch an accident, coroner rules
OL,6,FFollowing the inspection, there was a
OL,7,Frecommendation to remove ivy covering
OL,8,Fit to "aid future inspection" of the
OL,9,Ftree, which, after Brooke's death, was
OL,10,Frevealed to have had a "crack" not
OL,11,Fvisible from ground level.
OL,13,FA re-inspection was scheduled for May
OL,14,F2024, but this did not take place
OL,15,Fbecause of prioritising other
OL,16,Finspections, the inquest heard.
