OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1778170273
OL,3,CDeath of girl, 12, crushed by falling
OL,4,Ctree branch an accident, coroner rules
OL,6,FThe coroner told the inquest on
OL,7,FWednesday that there was "no sound
OL,8,Fevidence that a re-inspection by May
OL,9,F2024 would have revealed either a
OL,10,Fdangerous crack or a rope swing".
OL,12,FMr Collett said: "A criticism made in
OL,13,Fthis case of Surrey County Council has
OL,14,Fbeen that its inspection regime was
OL,15,Fdeficient. However, I do not make that
OL,16,Ffinding.
OL,26,@oD@ZOUrD@`O]tD@ROU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1778170273
OL,3,CDeath of girl, 12, crushed by falling
OL,4,Ctree branch an accident, coroner rules
OL,6,F"I accept the need to prioritise tree
OL,7,Finspection works. This is not the same
OL,8,Fstatutory territory as highway
OL,9,Finspection regimes, it is far more
OL,10,Fnuanced and must be far more reactive
OL,11,Fand flexible, especially given the
OL,12,Fresources available and the huge
OL,13,Fnumber of trees involved in the Surrey
OL,14,FCC estate."
OL,16,FThe inquest previously heard that a
OL,17,F"pathway for avoiding Brooke's death"
OL,18,Fwas for the erection of advisory
OL,19,Fnotices between May 2022 and May 2024
OL,20,Fwarning against rope swings.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@KO]yD@AOUyD@eO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1778170273
OL,3,CDeath of girl, 12, crushed by falling
OL,4,Ctree branch an accident, coroner rules
OL,6,FMr Collett rejected this in his
OL,7,Fconclusions because there was a lack
OL,8,Fof evidence that a rope swing would
OL,9,Fhave been discovered in that period
OL,10,Fand "it is doubtful that vigorous
OL,11,Fchildren and teenagers would take much
OL,12,Fnotice of warning signs".
OL,14,FThe assistant coroner told the inquest
OL,15,Fthat a Prevention of Future Deaths
OL,16,F(PFD) report was "not warranted" as
OL,17,F"there is a sufficient system already
OL,18,Fin place".
OL,20,FMr Collett ended the inquest by paying
OL,21,Ftribute to Brooke's family.
OL,26,@rD@EOUtD@XO]xD@ROUxD@`O]yD@AOUzD@IO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/8
