PN,40408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1778170273
OL,3,CDeath of girl, 12, crushed by falling
OL,4,Ctree branch an accident, coroner rules
OL,6,FHe said: "They have provided a voice
OL,7,Ffor her when she has been unable to
OL,8,Fspeak for herself.
OL,10,F"Brooke was plainly a light that shone
OL,11,Fin their lives, and while that light
OL,12,Fshone far less than half as long as
OL,13,Fwas its due, it clearly shone more
OL,14,Fthan twice as brightly."
